reviews.text:
I especially like it’s breakfast!
Actually I tried its dinner and lunch once, but compare to breakfast, breakfast is the best!

That’s why I always come for breakfast👍🏻👍🏻

The theme of the restaurant is about Old Master Q!  It is really suitable for parents and their kids!

The environment is nice, and you will feel relax while enjoying your food! 

The price of breakfast is reasonable!

And the quality of the food is good!

Some products are somewhat pricey, they may take a longer time to cook but the food there are yummy especially the meat they cook. Nice thick and juicy sauce. Not recommended if you are in a hurry, this is not a fast food restaurant + they only accept credit card for $100 or above

The quality of food is high, if the price could adjust down a little.  It can obtain the higher rating score.  However, the waiteesses seemed a little tried to provide the service, the smile faces were rare appeared here.
Food is served fast and of reasonable price. Nice themed restrauant

The dining room is set in the most iconic HK cartoon figures, known to old and young alike. The restaurant is relocated in the mall from their earlier operation in Prince Edward road. Love de decor, but service and menu are less impressive.

reviews.text: So many kind of shop.  All product are high quality.
it has good clothing items and also make up booths. They also have pop up shops sometimes

Mall 2 has sports shops such as gigasports with ok range of speed and arena brand swimming goggles and budget food options such as maccas and cafe de coral. To get there u have to walk through a ridiculous car park from yoho 1 if u come from mtr. U have to go up one level from mtr level to get there and u will most likely get lost even though it is simple layout. Cinema at one end of yoho 1 with yata.
